    "The joint probability of the token maps then factorizes over scales rather than token orders:p(r 1, r 2,..., r K) = K k=1 p(r k |r 1, r 2,..., r k-1).",
    "(2)with r k ∈ R h k ×w k ×D.",
    "This next-scale objective preserves spatial locality while preserving the unidirectional assumption for autoregressive models.Conditional Generation with VAR.",
